This repository contains configuration files, which are necessary to set up my personal Linux
environment - based on i3 windows manager and equipped with VIM text editor.


# Files description:

'i3_config' - i3 windows manager configuration, should be linked by ~/.config/i3/config
ln -s ~/config_scripts/i3_config ~/.config/i3/config

'i3status_config' - i3 status bar configuration, should be linked by ~/.config/i3status/config
ln -s ~/config_scripts/i3status_config ~/.config/i3status/config

'vimrc' - vim configuration file, should be linked by ~/.vim/vimrc
ln -s ~/config_scripts/vimrc ~/.vim/vimrc

'python.vim' - my own python vim plugin, should be linked by ~/.vim/ftplugin/python.vim
ln -s ~/config_scripts/python.vim ~/.vim/ftplugin/python.vim

'xinitrc' - X server init script, used to read resources, should be linked by ~/.xinitrc
ln -s ~/config_scripts/xinitrc ~/.xinitrc

'Xresources' - X server resources configuration, should be linked by ~/.Xresources
ln -s ~/config_scripts/Xresources ~/.Xresources



# VIM plugins to install

jedi-vim   (https://github.com/davidhalter/jedi-vim)
NERDTree   (https://github.com/preservim/nerdtree)
vim-flake8 (https://github.com/nvie/vim-flake8)



# Useful programs used with i3 windows manager

nm-applet
udiskie
i3lock
